<div class="row bg-xx-1 py-5 px-2">

    <div class="col-12 col-lg-4 text-center">
        <img src="~/images/look-up.png" class="img-intro" />
        <h3 class="h-intro text-white mt-2">Track</h3>
        <hr class="hr-intro bg-xx-6" />
        <p class="lead p-intro text-xx-6">
            Keep track of everything that makes Your hard earned stash get thinner. With ShopTracker you can record every individual
            purchase You make. To make the <i>Review</i> process even more rewarding You can specify where you bought it from and what
            was the currency of the payment, making vacation expense tracking piece of cake.
        </p>
    </div>

